{"id":241485,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/发现新闻-上海吴泾镇人民抗暴斗争――星星之火/","date":"2012-07-21T22:15:37Z","modified":"2012-07-21T22:15:37Z","title":"发现新闻 | 上海吴泾镇人民抗暴斗争――星星之火依然燎原（续）（多图）","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><strong>上海吴泾镇人民抗暴斗争――星星之火依然燎原（续）（多图）</strong></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><strong>――我们是二十一世纪的杨白劳</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><strong>（参与2012年7月21日讯）</strong>上海市闵行区吴泾镇政府、上海紫竹高科技园区官商勾结大搞圈地运动，违法征用耕地、宅基地，囤积土地。拆迁农民房屋安置补偿</span>70%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">面积，有许多农户几代人居住在拆迁后安置的蜗居内。在拆迁过程中，对农户进行威逼利诱；恐吓威胁；暗箱操作；欺下瞒上，动迁账目、合同阴阳，户与户之间补偿价格差距很大。相同面积竟然要相差</span>70<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">―</span>80<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万元人民币。吴泾镇土地被政府官员卖光了，村民的房屋也被拆光了，接下来政府官员挖空心思从村民身上刮民脂民膏，搞非法集资，镇政府利用镇开发办和资产办名义向村民非法集资敛财。镇政府推出所谓的《长效增收机制方案》。强迫村民签订协议，枪械易很神秘，两边有警察监视。签协议的村民要在</span>12<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">张纸上签名，</span>12<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">张纸上的内容不让看，对于不签名的村民对他们毁谤</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">造谣……。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"></span> </p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">村民们说：我们是二十一世纪的杨白劳。吴泾镇人民静坐抗议从</span> </p>\n<p>   2011<br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><br />\n   2<br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><br />\n   14<br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日</span><br />\n  <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">至</span></p>\n<p>   2012<br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><br />\n   7<br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><br />\n   21<br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日</span><br />\n  <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">有</span>526<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">天</span>.<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></p>\n<p> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><br />\n  <center><br />\n   <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121356306.jpg\" /><br />\n  </center></span><br />\n <span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><br />\n  <center><br />\n   <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121369934.jpg\" /><br />\n  </center></span><br />\n <center><br />\n  <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121368919.jpg\" /><br />\n </center> </p>\n<p>   </p>\n<p> <center><br />\n  <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121372347.jpg\" /><br />\n </center><br />\n <center><br />\n  <center><br />\n   <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121376296.jpg\" /><br />\n  </center><br />\n  <center><br />\n   上海星迎投资合伙企业（普通合伙） 合伙协议<br />\n  </center><br />\n  <center><br />\n   <center><br />\n    <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121427173.jpg\" /><br />\n   </center><br />\n   <center><br />\n    <center><br />\n     <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121421652.jpg\" /><br />\n    </center><br />\n   </center><br />\n  </center><br />\n  <center><br />\n   <center><br />\n    <img alt=\"\" align=\"center\" src=\"http://canyu.org/upload/2012_07/12072121434589.jpg\" /><br />\n   </center><br />\n  </center><br />\n  <center><br />\n   代持协议书<br />\n  </center><br />\n  <center><br />\n   <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">参与首发，转载请注明出处。（<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.canyu.org/\">www.canyu.org</a>）</span><br />\n  </center><br />\n </center></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/f0c27f8072121356306.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18269,10466],"tags":[19195]}